Doesn't matter if you are single or in relationship breaking OUR
VALENTINE hearts makes your day BETTER. It is just addictive tapping
fun and there is no need to feel guilty ?

~~ HOW TO PLAY? ~~
? 2 minutes finger exercise
? Make sure nobody is watching
? Use your lucky finger to hit HeartBreaker!
? Collect points by tapping hearts
? Beat the HighScore

